attributes.description:
## Polish Translator Responsibilities:
* translation and text editing from Polish into Russian/ Ukrainian and vice versa ( any other languages are appreciated);
* writing and editing articles for Internet resources;
* interpretation and translation in a timely manner;
* accurate translation with saving lexical, stylistic, grammar, and semantic content of the original;
* communication with clients.
As we operate in the international market, tasks may vary depending on the client's requirements.
## Requirements For A Polish Translator:
* Proficiency in Polish (knowledge of other languages is an advantage);
* confident PC user;
* clear and accurate solutions;
* responsible attitude to workflow;
* a strong sense of responsibility;
* eagerness to acquire new knowledge and develop skills.
If you have no experience as a Polish interpreter but have knowledge of a language or several languages, we are ready to consider your candidacy. Just record a video interview and send it to us. Don't miss the opportunity to work from home and get a steady salary.
Remote work from home means a comfortable work schedule: day shifts from 9:00 to 18:00, and evening shifts from 15:00 to 24:00. We guarantee on-time and decent wages.
Do you want to get a job as a Polish interpreter? Then record a
[video interview](/videointerview) and send it to us as soon as possible!
